examples.en: Her action amounted to a rebellion.
What is the amount to be paid?
An amount was finally agreed upon.
The drug is not being produced in adequate amounts.
The loans contracted had amounted to 530,000,000 francs.
When he died we found he owed money to the amount of $250,000!
The indebtedness of the bankrupt amounted to $1000.
The new law limits the amount a candidate can spend.
His care in observing the rules of good health amounted to a kind of religiousness.
